<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Mybatis </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">中进行查询操作的时候，查询单个对象、查询列表信息等的时候，我们需要每次都重复写创建</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">
                SqlSessionFactory</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">等相关代码</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#70ad47"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">// </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">根据主键</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> id </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">查询单个用户</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@Test</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">void
            testGet() throws Exception {</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#00b0f0">InputStream in =
                Resources.getResourceAsStream("mybatis-config.xml");</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#00b0f0">SqlSessionFactory sqlSessionFactory = new
                SqlSessionFactoryBuilder().build(in);</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#00b0f0">SqlSession sqlSession = sqlSessionFactory.openSession();</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">User
            user = sqlSession.selectOne("com.mxz.mybatis.mapper.UserMapper.get", 1L);</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#00b0f0">sqlSession.close();</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">}</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#70ad47"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">// </span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">查询所有用户</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@Test</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">void
            testListAll() throws Exception {</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#00b0f0">InputStream in =
                Resources.getResourceAsStream("mybatis-config.xml");</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#00b0f0">SqlSessionFactory sqlSessionFactory = new
                SqlSessionFactoryBuilder().build(in);</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#00b0f0">SqlSession sqlSession = sqlSessionFactory.openSession();</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">List&lt;User&gt; userList =
            sqlSession.selectList("com.mxz.mybatis.mapper.UserMapper.ListAll");</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#00b0f0">sqlSession.close();</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">}</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">这样一来，如果后面有多个操作的话，代码就显得很冗余，所以我们需要提取共同的代码，创建</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> MybatisUtil </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">类，把冗余的代码进行封装</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">这里边共同的代码主要是</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">加载构造器配置数据库交互文件（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSessionFactoryBuilder</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">创建构造器容器
                （</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSessionFactory</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">） </span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">数据库连接和操作的交互对象（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><img
        src="data:image/png;base64,"
        style="height:270px; width:410px"></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSessionFactoryBuilder</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">这个类可以被实例化、使用和丢弃，一旦创建了</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> SqlSessionFactory</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，就不再需要它了。</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">因此</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> SqlSessionFactoryBuilder </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的作用域是局部方法中</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSessionFactory</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSessionFactory
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">一旦被创建就应该在应用的运行期间一直存在，没有任何理由丢弃它或重新创建另一个实例，而使用（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">private
                static</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）共享</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">使用</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> SqlSessionFactory
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的最佳实践是在应用运行期间不要重复创建多次，因此使用单例模式或者静态单例模式控制只创建一次</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">每个线程都应该有它自己的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> SqlSession </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">实例。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的实例不是线程安全的，因此是不能被（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">public/private
                stastic</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）共享的，所以它的作用域是每个请求或每个方法的作用域中。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">绝对不能将</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> SqlSession </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">实例的引用放在一个类的静态域中共享</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">连接，甚至一个类的实例变量也不行。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;"><strong>注</strong></span></span>
</p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">所以，要记住的是，</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSessionFactory </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是线程安全的，和数据库连接池</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> dataSource </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">一样，整个应用中有一份就够了；</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SqlSession </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和数据库连接对象</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Connection </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是一样的，是线程不安全的，每次都要创建新的连接，用完了都要去关闭它，这个关闭操作是很重要的，你应该把这个关闭操作放到</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> finally </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">块中以确保每次都能执行关闭</span></span></p>
